This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and neural networks, specifically in the context of defining and using distance measures. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses applications of these distance measures in computer vision (cs.CV) and reinforcement learning (cs.AI, cs.NE), which are also likely categories. Finally, the paper includes theoretical results and proofs, which could place it in the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
